snippet.title: Out of Place Demo Teaser [Nordic Game 2019] - PC
snippet.description:
Watch the newest teaser of our overhauled demo version. Out of Place will be playable at the Nordic Game 2019 from 22-24 May at Slagthuset in Malmö, Sweden. Come and visit us there at the Unreal presents showcase, featured by Epic Games. 

More infos:

https://www.unrealengine.com/en-US/events/meet-up-with-epic-games-at-nordic-game-2019

Follow Simon's journey on social media 🎮🧑🗡️

https://discord.gg/hyFwqPC
https://twitter.com/OutofPlaceGame/
https://instagram.com/outofplacegame/
https://www.facebook.com/OutofPlaceGame/
